#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/macos.rst:4
msgid "Installing on macOS"
msgstr "Instal·lant en macOS"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/macos.rst:6
msgid ""
"Check the :doc:`Installing Blender </getting_started/installing/"
"introduction>` page to find the minimum requirements and where to get "
"Blender (if you have not done so yet)."
msgstr ""
"consulteu la página :doc:`Instal·lant Blender </getting_started/installing/"
"introduction>` per trobar els requisits mínims i on obtenir Blender (si "
"encara no ho heu fet)."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/macos.rst:9
msgid ""
"After downloading Blender for macOS, uncompress the file and drag ``blender."
"app`` into the Applications folder."
msgstr ""
"Després de descarregar Blender per MacOS, descomprimiu el fitxer i "
"arrossegueu ``blender.app`` a la carpeta d'aplicacions."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/macos.rst:13
msgid ""
"Blender does not use the standard macOS menu system so, you will likely have "
"a redundant menu-bar at the top."
msgstr ""
"Blender no utilitza el sistema de menú MacOS estàndard, així que "
"probablement tindreu una barra de menú redundant a la part superior."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/macos.rst:15
msgid ""
"To remove it see `this post <http://www.macworld.com/article/1055321/"
"hidemenubar.html>`__ on Macworld, but beware that it is somewhat complex. As "
"an alternative: simply make Blender full screen by :kbd:`Alt-F11` or by :"
"menuselection:`Info --> Window --> Toggle Window Fullscreen`."
msgstr ""
"Per treure-la, vegeu `aquesta entrada <http://www.macworld.com/"
"article/1055321/hidemenubar.html>`__ a Macworld, però tingueu en compte que "
"és una cosa complexa. Com a alternativa: simplement feu Blender a pantalla "
"completa mitjançant: :kbd:`Alt-F11` o :menuselection:`Info --> Finestra --> "
"Canvia a Pantalla Complerta`."
